{"type":"message","id":"d2c7ee5b","parentId":"e95ed2f6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:11:26.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提到技能和参数已配置，我需要先用 tushare 的通用行情接口获取自选股实时数据来排查问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我看到 tushare-data skill 已经配置好了。让我直接用 Python 脚本调用 tushare 接口获取你的自选股实时行情：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_070c6e97f4cb4abe808ab175","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 -c \"\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\n\n# 读取 TUSHARE_TOKEN 环境变量\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\nprint(f'Token: {\\\"已配置\\\" if token else \\\"未配置\\\"}')\n\nif token:\n    pro = ts.pro_api(token)\n    \n    # 股票列表\n    stocks = [\n        ('601857', '中国石油'),\n        ('601808', '中海油服'),\n        ('600256', '广汇能源'),\n        ('600583', '海油工程'),\n        ('000852', '石化机械'),\n        ('600547', '山东黄金'),\n        ('601069', '西部黄金'),\n        ('600988', '赤峰黄金'),\n        ('000975', '银泰黄金'),\n        ('002716', '金贵银业'),\n        ('601899', '紫金矿业'),\n    ]\n    \n    print('=' * 80)\n    print('Tushare 实时行情')\n    print('=' * 80)\n    \n    for code, name in stocks:\n        # 添加市场前缀\n        ts_code = f'{code}.SH' if code.startswith('6') else f'{code}.SZ'\n        \n        try:\n            # 使用实时日线接口\n            df = pro.daily_realtime(ts_code=ts_code)\n            if not df.empty:\n                close = df['close'].iloc[0]\n                change_pct = df['pct_chg'].iloc[0]\n                print(f'{code} {name:10s} | 现价：{close:.2f} | 涨跌：{change_pct:.2f}%')\n            else:\n                print(f'{code} {name:10s} | 无实时数据')\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f'{code} {name:10s} | 获取失败：{str(e)[:30]}')\n\"\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773040275152}}
